            "title": "Description & Details",
            "heading": "About the Product",
            "text": "<p>Rich marbling. Bold flavor. Our Prime Ribeye is cut from the finest USDA Prime beef for a steak that's tender, juicy, and full of flavor.<br\/><\/p><ul><li>USDA Prime, hand-selected<\/li><li>Well-marbled for maximum flavor<\/li><li>Wet-aged for tenderness<\/li><li>Cut fresh to order<\/li><\/ul>",
            "block_text_1": "<p><strong>Breed<\/strong><br\/>Black Angus<\/p>",
            "block_text_2": "<p><strong>Origin<\/strong><br\/>Victoria, Australia<\/p>",
            "block_text_3": "<p><strong>Age<\/strong><br\/>28-day dry-aged<\/p>",
            "block_text_4": "<p><strong>Marbling Score<\/strong><br\/>MB4+ (High)<\/p>",
            "block_text_5": "<p><strong>Feed<\/strong><br\/>100% Pasture-fed<\/p>",
            "block_text_6": "<p><strong>Hormones<\/strong><br\/>HGP-free<\/p>",
            "info_title": "Product Info",
            "product_info": "<p><strong>Grade:<\/strong> USDA Prime<\/p><p><strong>Cut:<\/strong> Ribeye<\/p><p><strong>Source:<\/strong> Midwestern, USA<br\/><br\/><strong>Aging:<\/strong> Wet-aged 21+ days<\/p><p><strong>Packaging:<\/strong> Vacuum sealed<\/p><p><strong>Freezer friendly:<\/strong> Yes<\/p>"
          }
        },
