1 11.7071C12.8946 11.5196 13 11.2652 13 11V5Z\" fill=\"CurrentColor\"\/>\n<\/svg>",
            "title": "Preparation",
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Rectangle_25.png",
            "text": "<p><strong>Thaw in refrigerator.<\/strong><br\/>Remove fillets from plastic wrap.<br\/><br\/><strong>Bake:<\/strong><br\/>Preheat oven to 400 °F. Place salmon fillets on a foil lined baking sheet. Bake for 10 to 12 minutes.<br\/><br\/><strong>Grill:<\/strong><br\/>Grill salmon fillets over medium heat 4 to 5 minutes per side.<br\/><br\/><strong>Microwave:<\/strong><br\/>Place salmon fillets in a microwave safe dish. Cover with plastic wrap, venting one corner.<br\/>Microwave on high 3 to 4  minutes, rotating halfway through cooking.<br\/><br\/><strong>Air Fryer (1500 Watt):<\/strong><br\/>Preheat air fryer to 350°F. Lightly  spray basket with nonstick cooking spray. Remove salmon from packaging  and place desired number of servings in air fryer, leaving 1\/2\" between  pieces. Cook for 10-12 minutes or until temperature reaches 145°F.<\/p>"
          }
        },
